{"tid":2105822,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"職業治療OT Research x Dating","createTime":"2020-07-13T02:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T01:55:04.000Z","uid":117366,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"51896c74a0e9725c059057fc0422b23fa367e19a","tid":2105822,"uid":117366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T02:02:48.000Z","msg":"如果屋企冇乜野做，又想分享你自己嘅經歷，不彷將自己嘅經歷變做文字幫下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係職業治療final year student，做緊有關dating嘅研究<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我需要大家嘅故事啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請通過以下鏈結填寫問卷：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sydneyhealthsciences.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_06SCLgG06S0izFX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsydneyhealthsciences.au1.qualtrics.com%2Fjfe%2Fform%2FSV_06SCLgG06S0izFX&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZosxvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=ef326734\" target=\"_blank\">https://sydneyhealthsciences.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_06SCLgG06S0izFX</a><br />\n<br />\n最後亦希望你能幫我們轉發並分享給您身邊周圍的人，讓我們能收集到不同人（年齡，種族，性取向，宗教等）的故事💁。<br />\n<br />\n琴晚比人係創意台借刀，搞到係咁比人spam條link. 希望今日唔會喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52360f45c32d93daf9e404f2096d1c28c1f77d56","tid":2105822,"uid":132655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T02:24:00.000Z","msg":"click咗入去填到第二版，發覺太多字要填，走先<br />\n<br />\n認真咁多詳細嘢要填好趕客，返工無可能逐個問題打字"},{"pid":"ff8ac753a2e8ef9035441a5d6a0ce6361241165f","tid":2105822,"uid":117366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"52360f45c32d93daf9e404f2096d1c28c1f77d56","tid":2105822,"uid":132655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T02:24:00.000Z","msg":"click咗入去填到第二版，發覺太多字要填，走先<br />\n<br />\n認真咁多詳細嘢要填好趕客，返工無可能逐個問題打字"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T02:31:17.000Z","msg":"絕對明啊，可以有時間再入番條link繼續 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為每個人ge經歷都好唔